message.content: The paper belongs to the arXiv CS sub-category "cs.CL" (Computation and Language) as it deals with natural language processing techniques for biomedical question answering. Other likely sub-categories could be "cs.IR" (Information Retrieval) as the paper involves retrieving relevant snippets from multiple documents, "cs.LG" (Machine Learning) as the paper explores the use of deep learning architectures, "cs.AI" (Artificial Intelligence) as the paper deals with intelligent systems for question answering, and "cs.CV" (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition) as the paper involves text summarization techniques which can be seen as a form of image compression.
